      <title>欧洲央行会议召开前，意大利债券发行需求创纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/italy-gets-record-130-billion-bids-for-30-year-debt-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利新发售的 30 年期债券吸引了超过 1,300 亿欧元（1,440 亿美元）的订单，投资者纷纷赶在本周晚些时候欧洲央行预期降息之前锁定该地区最高收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/italy-gets-record-130-billion-bids-for-30-year-debt-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风力发电抑制需求导致欧洲天然气价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/european-gas-prices-push-higher-as-cold-snap-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格有望四个交易日以来首次下跌，原因是可再生能源发电量增强抑制了需求，且交易商正在关注热带风暴弗朗辛的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/european-gas-prices-push-higher-as-cold-snap-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
